1.00	The_Hard_Road_(song)	The Hard Road (song)	"The Hard Road" is a song by Australian hip hop band Hilltop Hoods. It is the second single taken from on their 2006 album of the same name. The theme of the song relates to growing up and living in a city, having no direction in life and dealing with the troublesome life associated with urban culture. The song contains a sample of "Out in the Woods", originally by Leon Russell.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/83/TheHardRoad.jpg/220px-TheHardRoad.jpg
